      },
      "dc:title": "FAIR Metric - DOI metadata contains a link to a community ontology term - PaNET",
      "http://vivoweb.org/ontology/core#abbreviation": "FM_I2_M_VOC-PANET_DOI_ESRF",
      "dc:description": " This metric ensures that the research object provided by the supplied URL is associated with a DataCite DOI whose metadata contains a PaNET subject term. This means that the DataCite metadata for the research object’s DOI must define a subject from PaNET using schemeUri or subjectScheme. The supplied URL can be one of: a doi.org domain URL or a DOI target repository domain URL.",
